import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import image from './123.jpg';
import './Sign-Up.css'


const Signup = () => {

    var Shadow = {
        boxShadow: "25px 25px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15)"

    };

    return ( <
        div className = 'container ' >
        <
        div style = {
            Shadow
        }
        className = "center p-4 img-cover shadow "
        style = {
            {
                backgroundImage: `url(${image})`
            }
        } >


        <
        Form >
        <
        Form.Group controlId = "formFile"
        className = "mb-5" >
        <
        Form.Control type = "file" /
        >

        <
        h3 className = "mt-3 text-center " > Sign Up < /h3> <
        /Form.Group> <
        Row className = "mb-1 " >
        <
        Form.Group as = {
            Col
        }
        controlId = "exampleForm.ControlInput1" >
        <
        Form.Label > Firstname: < /Form.Label> <
        Form.Control className = 'border-start-0 border-top-0 border-end-0'
        type = "text"
        placeholder = "Enter your Name" /
        >
        <
        /Form.Group>

        <
        Form.Group as = {
            Col
        }
        controlId = "exampleForm.ControlInput1" >
        <
        Form.Label > Lastname: < /Form.Label> <
        Form.Control className = 'border-start-0 border-top-0 border-end-0'
        type = "text"
        placeholder = "Enter your Name" /
        >
        <
        /Form.Group> <
        /Row>

        <
        Form.Group className = "mb-1"
        controlId = "formBasicEmail" >
        <
        Form.Label > Email address < /Form.Label> <
        Form.Control type = "email"
        placeholder = "Enter email"
        className = 'border-start-0 border-top-0 border-end-0' /
        >

        <
        /Form.Group>

        <
        Form.Group className = "mb-1"
        controlId = "formBasicPassword" >
        <
        Form.Label > Password < /Form.Label> <
        Form.Control type = "password"
        placeholder = "Password"
        className = 'border-start-0 border-top-0 border-end-0' /
        >
        <
        /Form.Group>


        <
        Form.Group className = "mb-1"
        controlId = "formBasicPassword" >
        <
        Form.Label > Confirm Password < /Form.Label> <
        Form.Control type = "password"
        placeholder = "Password"

        /
        >
        <
        /Form.Group> <
        Form.Group className = "mb-1"
        controlId = "formBasicCheckbox" >

        <
        /Form.Group>

        <
        div className = "d-grid gap-2" >
        <
        Button className = "shadow mt-5 btn-md"
        variant = "secondary"
        type = "submit" >
        Sign Up Now <
        /Button> <
        /div> <
        /Form >

        <
        >

        <
        /> <
        /div> <
        /div >

    )

}


export default Signup
